<feed xml:lang="en" xmlns="http://www.w3.org/2005/Atom"><title>边缘 - 所有帖子</title><icon>https://cdn.vox-cdn.com/community_logos/52801/VER_Logomark_32x32..png</icon><updated> 2024-12-03T05:00:00-05:00</updated><id> https://www.theverge.com/rss/full.xml</id><link href="https://www.theverge.com/" rel="alternate" type="text/html"/><entry><published> 2024-12-03T05:00:00-05:00</published><updated> 2024-12-03T05:00:00-05:00</updated><title>数据经纪人可能被禁止出售您的社会安全号码</title><content type="html">&lt;figure>; &lt;img alt=&quot;挂锁和链条旁边的像素化钥匙插图，暗示在线数据安全。&quot; src =“https://cdn.vox-cdn.com/thumbor/R4MjSj6krABAZqVnYCl9SJymHZI=/20x0:2021x1334/1310x8 73/cdn.vox-cdn.com/uploads/chorus_image/image/73762823/STK453_Privacy_D_CVirginia.0.jpg&quot; />; &lt;figcaption>;Cath Virginia / The Verge |照片：Getty Images&lt;/figcaption>; &lt;/figure>; &lt;p id=&quot;vBDsn0&quot;>;在影响数亿美国人的备受瞩目的黑客攻击之后，消费者金融保护局 (CFPB) 提出了一项限制数据经纪人的规则&#39; 出售美国人敏感个人和财务信息的能力。&lt;/p>; &lt;p id=&quot;rd0yyn&quot;>;根据拟议规则，出售有关消费者收入、信用记录、信用评分或债务支付信息的数据经纪人将被禁止考虑消费者报告机构。因此，他们必须遵守《公平信用报告法》(FCRA)，该法律限制这些机构获取和使用消费者报告中提供的信息的方式。换句话说，他们将被视为信用局和背景调查公司，它们已经必须遵守 FCRA。&lt;/p>; &lt;p id=&quot;aKmiXE&quot;>;在...&lt;/p>; &lt;p>; &lt;a href=&quot;https://www.theverge.com/2024/12/3/24311498/cfpb-rule-data-brokers-social-security-number-fico-score&quot;>;继续阅读……&lt;/a>; &lt;/p>; </content><link href="https://www.theverge.com/2024/12/3/24311498/cfpb-rule-data-brokers-social-security-number-fico-score" rel="alternate" type="text/html"/><id> https://www.theverge.com/2024/12/3/24311498/cfpb-rule-data-brokers-social-security-number-fico-score</id><author><name>盖比·德尔·瓦莱</name></author></entry><entry><published>2024-12-03T00:58:32-05:00</published><updated> 2024-12-03T00:58:32-05:00</updated><title>您仍然可以购买网络星期一最后一刻的最佳优惠</title><content type="html">&lt;figure>; &lt;img alt=&quot;浏览器窗口中排列的网络星期一销售产品的插图。&quot; src =“https://cdn.vox-cdn.com/thumbor/eN-C8Y4oBM5R56F-wkCPw4_952g=/0x0:2040x1360/1310x873/cd n.vox-cdn.com/uploads/chorus_image/image/73756741/247350_C