。&lt;/p>; &lt;p id=&quot;HSgjDR&quot;>;这一承诺也延伸到了 Windows 方面的变化： GOG 表示，影响游戏的可玩性。&lt;/p>; &lt;div class=&quot;c-float-left c-float-hang&quot;>;&lt;aside id=&quot;lAdMGz&quot;>;&lt;div data-anthem-component=&quot;readmore&quot; data-anthem-component-data=&#39;{&quot;stories&quot;:[{&quot;title&quot;:&quot;GOG 的新保存计划旨在让经典游戏‘永远’保持可玩性”,&quot;url&quot;:&quot;https://www.theverge.com /2024/11/13/24295683/gog-preservation-program-pc-game-drm&quot;},{&quot;title&quot;:&quot;魔兽争霸 I 和 II 获得了新的重制版现在&quot;,&quot;url&quot;:&quot;https://www.theverge.com/2024/11/13/24295730/warcraft-remastered-battle-chest-1-2-3-reforged-upgrades-windows-mac-blizzard- Battle-net&quot;}]}&#39;>;&lt;/div>;&lt;/aside>;&lt;/div>; &lt;p id=&quot;5TTgCy&quot;>;保存计划 &lt;a href=&quot;https://www.theverge.com/2024/11/13/24295683/gog-preservation-program-pc-game-drm&quot;>;上个月推出&lt;/a>;，提供持续的技术支持和兼容性更新一些经典游戏。 GOG 一开始就列出了 100 款游戏，包括《暗黑破坏神》和《生化危机 1-3》。&lt;/p>; &lt;p id=&quot;yT7eGB&quot;>;&lt;em>;魔兽争霸 I该公司表示，“应发行商的要求”，《魔兽争霸 II》和《魔兽争霸 II》将被从 GOG 上除名。他们的出版商...&lt;/p>; &lt;p>; &lt;a href=&quot;https://www.theverge.com/2024/12/2/24311537/gog-preservation-program-warcraft-1-2-delisted-支持-继续&quot;>;继续阅读&amp;hellip;&lt;/a>; &lt;/p>; </content><link href="https://www.theverge.com/2024/12/2/24311537/gog-preservation-program-warcraft-1-2-delisted-support-continues" rel="alternate" type="text/html"/><id> https://www.theverge.com/2024/12/2/24311537/gog-preservation-program-warcraft-1-2-delisted-support-continues</id><author><name>韦斯·戴维斯</name></author></entry><entry><published>2024-12-02T18:27:43-05:00</published><updated> 2024-12-02T18:27:43-05:00</updated><title>联想 Legion Go S 泄露展示了更便宜的手持游戏电脑的渲染图</title><content type="html">&lt;figure>; &lt;img alt=&quot;legion go s 游戏手持设备的正面、背面和顶部，每个按钮和端口都有编号标签&quot; src =“https://cdn.vox-cdn.com/thumbor/kAS00rgot_vQkfyKnvKwdTr7OQ0=/0x0:3950x2633/1310x873/cdn .vox-cdn.com/uploads/chorus_image/image/73762231/Screenshot_2024_12_02_at_5.43.49_PM.0.jpeg&quot; />; &lt;figcaption>;&lt;em>;看